# Day 37 – Task Compass using Claude AI

## Objective

Built an interactive Task Compass application to understand how work flows through organizations by exploring ownership, delegation, collaboration, and task routing.

## Features

- Workplace Type Selection
- Stage 1: Who Owns This?
- Stage 2: Task Routing
- Stage 3: Collaboration Challenge
- Organizational Thinking Dashboard
- Reflection & Insights
- Drag-and-Drop Interactions
- Responsive UI
- Replay Functionality

## Tech Stack

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Key Learnings

- Workplace tasks often require collaboration across multiple roles.
- Clear ownership improves accountability.
- Effective task routing enhances workflow efficiency.
- Organizational success depends on communication and teamwork.

